race.description: Girls Day Out On Sale Now Plate (C1)
race.comment: FIREFORCE (3) looks to be building up to another victory with consecutive runner-up finishes this time in work and will strip fitter third-up from the break. Has placed three of five over this distance range and should be right there at the business end. DATA SCRAMBLE (10) was a touch disappointing at the latest effort but the two runs prior to start the campaign were good enough for a race of this nature. Worth another chance. HEAVENLY IMPACT (4) is drawn to get a gun run in transit from the inside alley and must be included in exotics. CASTELLO GRANDE (6) next best from the Heathcote yard following a recent trial placing at Doomben. Can figure in the finish
